<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8"/>
    <title>Top of the Poops - Support, Sponsor or Subscribe</title>
    <meta name="description" content="Analysing sewage dumps by water companies in the UK">

    {{> chunks/favicons }}
    {{> chunks/meta-styles }}
    {{> chunks/meta-scripts }}

    {{> components/meta-opengraph
            title="Support & Subscriptions"
            twitterImageUri=share.twitterImageUri
    }}

    <style>
        .card {
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            border: none;
        }

        .support-icon {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }

        .card-header {
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        .responsive-iframe {
            border: 0;
            max-width: 100%;
        }

        .iframe-container {
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
            width: 100%;
        }

        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .responsive-iframe {
                min-height: 700px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
{{> chunks/navbar }}

{{#> components/jumbotron }}
    <div class="text-center py-4">
        <h1 class="display-3 fw-bold mb-4">We Need Your Support!</h1>
        <p class="lead fs-3 mb-4">
            Help us continue tracking sewage pollution and holding water companies accountable
        </p>
        <div class="d-flex justify-content-center gap-3">
            <i class="bi bi-heart-fill text-danger fs-1"></i>
            <i class="bi bi-water text-primary fs-1"></i>
            <i class="bi bi-heart-fill text-danger fs-1"></i>
        </div>
    </div>
{{/components/jumbotron}}

<script async
        src="https://js.stripe.com/v3/buy-button.js">
</script>


<div class="container py-4">

    <div class="row justify-content-md-center mb-5">
        <div class="col-md-8">
            <div class="card border-0 bg-light shadow-sm">
                <div class="card-body p-4">
                    <div class="text-center mb-4">
                        <i class="bi bi-info-circle-fill text-primary support-icon"></i>
                        <h2 class="fw-bold">Why We Need Your Help</h2>
                    </div>
                    <p class="lead">Running a website with this much information costs money. Server maintenance,
                        design, and programming are all expensive investments that help us track pollution
                        effectively.</p>
                    <div class="row mt-4">
                        <div class="col-md-6">
                            <div class="d-flex mb-3">
                                <div class="me-3">
                                    <i class="bi bi-graph-up-arrow text-success fs-4"></i>
                                </div>
                                <div>
                                    <h5>Develop More Sources</h5>
                                    <p>Your support helps us expand our data collection and analysis capabilities.</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-md-6">
                            <div class="d-flex mb-3">
                                <div class="me-3">
                                    <i class="bi bi-bell text-warning fs-4"></i>
                                </div>
                                <div>
                                    <h5>Pollution Alerts</h5>
                                    <p>We're developing real-time notification services for river pollution.</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="alert alert-info mt-3">
                        <div class="d-flex">
                            <div class="me-2">
                                <i class="bi bi-shield-check fs-4"></i>
                            </div>
                            <div>
                                <p class="mb-0"><strong>Your Privacy Matters:</strong> We won't add you to any mailing
                                    lists unless you choose to join the mailing list. You can cancel subscriptions at any time with no
                                    notice.</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <p class="text-center mt-4 mb-0 fw-bold fs-5">Thank you for your support!</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <h2 class="text-center mb-4 fw-bold">Choose Your Support Method</h2>

    <div class="row g-4">
        <div class="col-md-4 mb-3">
            <div class="card h-100 text-center shadow-sm">
                <div class="card-header bg-primary text-white py-3">
                    <h4 class="mb-0"><i class="bi bi-credit-card me-2"></i>Stripe</h4>
                </div>
                <div class="card-body p-4">
                    <div class="mb-3">
                        <i class="bi bi-arrow-repeat text-primary support-icon"></i>
                    </div>
                    <h5 class="card-title mb-3">Monthly Subscription</h5>
                    <p class="card-text mb-4">Subscribe as a Top-of-the-Poops supporter with a small monthly payment.
                        Cancel anytime with no questions asked. Supporters get first access to new features including
                        real-time pollution alerts.<br/>
                    <em class="fw-bold">To support us for more than Â£1/month - just update the 'Quantity' in the Stripe checkout field.</em>
                    </p>



                    <stripe-buy-button
                            buy-button-id="buy_btn_1PuHaFI1rZXPCk5qWxlwBBIb"
                            publishable-key="pk_live_51PuHKQI1rZXPCk5q9GUWxgUcSqKzIDqeo9JK7wFDjZwVKKcwks3PKCSJix9zbevhuhggUUHR9DiEmXdKDk1nqRNy00Ko01Hebm"
                    >
                    </stripe-buy-button>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="col-md-4 mb-3">
            <div class="card h-100 text-center shadow-sm">
                <div class="card-header bg-success text-white py-3">
                    <h4 class="mb-0"><i class="bi bi-cash-coin me-2"></i>GoFundMe</h4>
                </div>
                <div class="card-body p-4">
                    <div class="mb-3">
                        <i class="bi bi-piggy-bank text-success support-icon"></i>
                    </div>
                    <h5 class="card-title mb-3">One-Time Donation</h5>
                    <p class="card-text mb-4">Make a one-off payment to help support our work. It's quick, easy, and
                        every contribution makes a difference in our fight against water pollution.</p>

                    {{> components/gofundme text="Support on GoFundMe"}}
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="col-md-4 mb-3">
            <div class="card h-100 text-center shadow-sm">
                <div class="card-header bg-warning text-dark py-3">
                    <h4 class="mb-0"><i class="bi bi-github me-2"></i>GitHub Sponsor</h4>
                </div>
                <div class="card-body p-4">
                    <div class="mb-3">
                        <i class="bi bi-code-square text-warning support-icon"></i>
                    </div>
                    <h5 class="card-title mb-3">Support Open Source</h5>
                    <p class="card-text mb-4">For the tech-savvy, GitHub Sponsors allows people with a GitHub account or
                        organisation to sponsor our Open Source technology and development.</p>

                    <a target="_blank" href="https://github.com/sponsors/top-poop">
                        <button class="btn btn-warning btn-lg px-4" aria-label="Sponsor @top-poop on GitHub">
                            <i class="bi bi-heart-fill me-2"></i>
                            <span>Sponsor on GitHub</span>
                        </button>
                    </a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="row justify-content-center mt-5 pt-4 border-top">
        <div class="col-md-8">
            <div class="text-center mb-4">
                <i class="bi bi-envelope-paper text-info support-icon"></i>
                <h2 class="fw-bold">Stay Informed</h2>
                <p class="lead">Join our email list to receive updates about water pollution and our ongoing work</p>
            </div>

            <div class="card shadow-sm">
                <div class="card-header bg-info text-white py-3">
                    <h4 class="mb-0 text-center"><i class="bi bi-envelope-check me-2"></i>Email Newsletter</h4>
                </div>
                <div class="card-body p-4 text-center">
                    <p class="mb-4">Sign up to get more information about pollution in rivers and seas, campaign
                        updates, and ways you can help make a difference.</p>

                    <div class="iframe-container">
                        <iframe class="responsive-iframe" style="min-height: 650px; width: 100%;"
                                src="https://cdn.forms-content-1.sg-form.com/ddd499f1-948a-11ef-832c-c6e07dcc13bd">
                            Our sign-up page is here but your browser isn't displaying it.
                        </iframe>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>


{{> chunks/footer }}


</body>
</html>
